Creating Logical Volumn
  lsblk - to see existing partition 
  1.creating PV
    - partition disks
    - pvcreate <partition_disk...>
  2.creating VG
    - vgcreate [-s PE_size] <VG_name>  <PV...>
    - vgcreate 
  3.creating LV
    - lvcreate  <-L size> <VG_name>
    
Growing VG LV
  - lvextend -L 4g -v /dev/vg00/lvol0
  - vgextend vg00 /dev/sdn1
